INSTALL:

Unpack the archive into a directory, put your own settings into BotConfig.hs
then run:

	autoconf
	./configure
	make	(gmake on some systems)

KNOWN BUGS:
* @topic often returns nothing, no idea why

Bug reports, patches, new modules etc, contact:

	Don Stewart <dons@cse.unsw.edu.au>
	aka dons on #haskell

Check out our darcs repo at:
http://www.cse.unsw.edu.au/~dons/lambdabot
http://www.ScannedInAvian.org/repos/lambdabot
